              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37993617/" class="">第82页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sissiangel1988/" class=" " title="SHAERO">SHAERO</a>
                (兵来将挡who怕who)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
